  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e39e78da-b707-462a-95a2-4dbaaeee0ea2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-227b64ea-fbca-4fc8-87fa-841aad7e92dc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f63bdcb0-f144-48b9-8e80-eb12dbdb37ed\">어려서부터 손발이 찬 경우도 있지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7a4b4709-60f1-42cd-b6ea-3277ac672d36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dfba5f15-1727-48cd-9649-a606bebee156\">성인이 된 후, 어느순간부터 손발이 차가워지는 분들도 있죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d37ff5b6-9478-4802-b4a2-25ac0fe83d3c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-394c6057-137b-4a19-9a6f-207bb9dc4ead\">여름에도 힘들지만, 겨울에는 손발이 시려서 큰 고통을 격습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b67af3f7-c760-43b2-a9f0-823c73bf361d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ab7278c-9437-490c-b95c-86affe8140a3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8dd4ed69-91a9-4a0e-9020-f19fa14f6bbe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5048fab1-8a5a-4f04-a78a-9b285ddaa8d1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e1dceba-c69d-4e45-9a39-0d9af5483394\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f460892a-49ef-49b7-959c-2554880133e2\">수족냉증 설명은 아래 그림을 보시죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5af1b2c5-09fd-480c-bca9-d04fe254391b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5af1b2c5-09fd-480c-bca9-d04fe254391b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eaf230f99d01134b.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2480\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3507\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eaf230f99d01134b.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eaf230f99d01134b.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3484ebd3-85cb-4e04-ac4d-f04cc6db10b2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-457048c3-c6d1-4bbe-908c-8eb1468dfe20\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-31348332-9e41-40f6-b633-d8e239a82646\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-65635f3f-d7e0-43da-83f2-77f516161e3f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b19b39d1-b86f-4657-b899-a759ac7e9f73\">경험상, 수족냉증은 체질과 관련되는 경우가 많았습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-623239c4-7306-4231-b9ef-d9970aa3bcd7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0a4f83e6-297a-4474-9dcc-229fefffd270\">그래서 체질을 개선하는 치료를 하면 호전됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-48da22e9-7f4f-42e9-a5b3-01508e81ff9f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3c42f87-c8d8-418b-a0f5-885c3d91bdf6\">(안타깝지만, 수족냉증의 원인에 따라 치료가 안되는 경우도 있습니다)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d33a09b2-4d52-4c9a-ade1-4ab366537f6a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-21751561-8088-4c31-88d8-e536dc3a64f6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfee0266-1dd3-4661-8373-3c85da84f8af\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1d392f26-db2f-4747-b246-f4dcbbcf93fd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20ff0f47-6062-40b0-b328-739422d9f725\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd00a62a-d32d-482e-bbac-8910314f719c\">수족냉증의 관리는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a614b0c3-6744-405f-a010-eb0741f3d55e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4b8cddd-e6a0-4dc2-a8f7-5